{"tid":1109700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"完整分析安心偷食一事","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T10:56:04.000Z","uid":203736,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db30afd0992d130611dfd16fd824c5420504f5ad","tid":1109700,"uid":203736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"點解要去偷食？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊脷。<br />\n我好妥你，我可以咀你；<br />\n我好鍾意你，我可以摸你。<br />\n馬明你睥咩呀？出嚟戴帽吖！<br />\n戴帽呀！<br />\n戴住吖！戴吖！<br />\n我戴你你戴帽，點呀？<br />\n你見過杜生未呀？你見過一智未呀？<br />\n你話馬國明你偶像吖嘛，你見過馬國明未呀？<br />\n杜德偉蔡一智吖嘛，好巴閉呀？<br />\n你知唔知佢條女畀人摸咗佢掹唔到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢條女，帽，佢戴實晒。<br />\n你知唔知馬國明諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢唔想戴頂綠帽，<br />\n佢唔想畀人綠帽，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偷食，我都有。<br />\n其實，戴唔戴帽，我理唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，戴綠帽，冇得返轉頭。"},{"pid":"7ac852ef487e5ff7fdf74c8edb3aa2c067fc4124","tid":1109700,"uid":197857,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"無幽默感就自覺d收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae2a75f3d8bcdf9334a3fc3fe08be6fee0f69b8","tid":1109700,"uid":228831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad86aef085376859d1fa69b7132f39529329d6d3","tid":1109700,"uid":203736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ac852ef487e5ff7fdf74c8edb3aa2c067fc4124","tid":1109700,"uid":197857,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"無幽默感就自覺d收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"想知巴打有何高見 畀小弟可以改進一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}